Hi Mark,

YES!!!!

My 1973/74/79 Westfakia has Jalousie windows that came from my late 73
westy.

AFAIK all the bay's have identical glass, except that late (2L) bays got
sliding side windows and earlier bays had optional vent wings on the
driver's side.


